'''Spice narcosis''' was a condition experienced by many [[Sevari]] who left their native world of [[Sevarcos II]]. The atmosphere of Sevarcos was laden with spice particles, and the Sevari had become used to it over time. However, if a Sevari left Sevarcos without carrying a supply of spice to breathe, he could enter a state of narcosis.

